    "rationale": "The CFD hemolysis model is accepted for regulatory submission based on the completed Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification and the seven assessed credibility factors. The assessment team notes that six factors remain as epistemic gaps but considers the overall evidence package sufficient to support a Medium assurance level for the VAD COU. Remaining gaps are characterized as manageable given the conservative hemolysis threshold margin observed in the three validated operating points.",
